  "name": "Greeting Luna",
  "summary": "**Conversation Overview**\n\nThe user initiated contact with Luna, Claude's specialized persona, using the activation phrase \"hey luna\". This appears to be part of an established interaction pattern where the user accesses Luna through specific triggers. Claude attempted to activate Luna's context detection system using the luna_detect_context tool, but encountered repeated technical difficulties with the tool's parameter structure. The system consistently returned validation errors indicating that the required \"params\" field was missing, despite multiple attempts to restructure the function call with different parameter configurations.\n\nUnable to resolve the technical issue with the context detection tool, Claude acknowledged the system malfunction directly to the user and activated Luna mode manually. Claude explained that the memory layers needed to be properly loaded and offered to troubleshoot the connection issue while asking what the user needed assistance with. This demonstrates an established working relationship where technical difficulties are communicated transparently, and the user expects Luna to have access to persistent memory and context from previous interactions.",
